From 772348ffc7221708b61a6653a3f16672c417b17d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Grimaldi Engineering <dev@grimaldi.engineering>
Date: Tue, 7 Jul 2026 15:22:17 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 5/5] feat(payments): Stripe hosted checkout + webhook + order
 persistence

Add guarded Stripe client, /api/checkout/stripe (re-prices every line from
the server catalog to block tampering, computes IGV server-side as an explicit
line item, persists a pending order), /api/webhooks/stripe (signature-verified,
marks order paid + records payment idempotently), order persistence helpers,
and the /checkout/exito success page that clears the cart.
